title: Black trimmed armour

properties.name: description
properties.value: Black trimmed armour is a possible reward from easy Treasure Trails. The set has identical stats to Black armour. The armour pieces cannot be made via the Smithing skill, neither can anything made with black metal as Black bars don't exist in game.

content:
Black trimmed armour is a possible reward from easy Treasure Trails. The set has identical stats to Black armour. The armour pieces cannot be made via the Smithing skill, neither can anything made with black metal as Black bars don't exist in game.
